OL,4,Cwas 'not being medicated' for psychosis
OL,6,FA woman who killed a pensioner in a Co-
OL,7,Fop store in Penygraig, Rhondda Cynon
OL,8,FTaff 'was not being medicated' for her
OL,9,Fpsychosis and her 'risk of harm to
OL,10,Fothers was insufficiently assessed',
OL,11,Fan inquest has concluded.
OL,13,F88-year-old John Rees died after Zara
OL,14,FRadcliffe attacked him inside the shop
OL,15,Fand repeatedly struck him to the head
OL,16,Fwith wine bottles and a fire
OL,17,Fextinguisher.
