OL,6,FAyette Bounouri was in the shop and
OL,7,Fconfronted Zara Radcliffe. Ayette and
OL,8,Fanother woman, Lisa Way, stepped in
OL,9,Fwhile Mr Rees was being attacked,
OL,10,Fusing a sandwich delivery crate as a
OL,11,Fshield.
OL,13,FSpeaking outside the coroner's court,
OL,14,Fshe said, "You do not feel scared.
OL,15,FThings happen so fast and you're so
OL,16,Fdetermined to protect the life of
OL,17,Fsomeone and yourself that you don't
OL,18,Fhave time to feel any fear. The
OL,19,Fadrenaline takes over.
