OL,6,F"It's probably a few days later that
OL,7,Fyou realise the impact it's had on
OL,8,Fmyself, on the community, and then you
OL,9,Fstart having trauma symptoms.
OL,11,F"After sitting here for four days
OL,12,Flistening to all the evidence, it was
OL,13,Falong process but a necessary process
OL,14,Fthat will inform changes, and we will
OL,15,Flearn from it.
OL,17,F"It will be with us for the rest of
OL,18,Four lives."
