OL,6,FMr Rees, Ms Bonouri, and Ms Way were
OL,7,Fall awarded the Queen's Gallantry
OL,8,FMedal for bravery for their role in
OL,9,Fhelping save the lives of other people
OL,10,Fin the shop.
OL,12,FAfter her arrest, Zara Radcliffe told
OL,13,Fpolice she had been hearing voices
OL,14,Ftelling her to kill someone or she
OL,15,Fwould be killed herself.
OL,17,FShe pleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,18,Fwas detained under a hospital order in
OL,19,FOctober 2020.
