OL,4,Cwas 'not being medicated' for psychosis
OL,6,FThe inquest also heard that Zara had a
OL,7,Fhistory of violence and was prescribed
OL,8,Fanti-psychotic medication but she was
OL,9,Fdischarged from the hospital just over
OL,10,Ftwo months before the attack.
OL,12,FHer father has previously told ITV
OL,13,FWales that on the morning of the
OL,14,Fattack, he had tried to contact social
OL,15,Fservices as he was worried his
OL,16,Fdaughter was "seriously ill". He
OL,17,Fbelieves "if Zara had had the help she
OL,18,Fneeded, this wouldn't have happened."
